Welcome to the Fourth Keulė Rūkė BBQ House - Animal Farm.Keulė Rūkė is a American (BBQ) tradition restaurant opened in Vilnius at the beginning of 2015. From September Keulė Rūkė can be found in Kaunas, Urmo base, Pramonės pr. 16A every day from 11 am. to 24 pm.At Keulė Rūkė you can taste a real American BBQ. Barbecue is the slow process - selected pork is spoiled with a mixture of home-made spices and are smoked in oven with genuine oak wood at low temperatures for more than ten hours. After such heat treatment and long baking, the meat fumes smoke and is particularly easy to remove from bones - this is the main attribute of meat processed with barbecue technology. If there is no smoke, it's not a real barbecue.


